title: HOUR 3- Erik Bacharach and Tom Curran Oct 08, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Erik Bacharach and Tom Curran Oct 08, 2020
description:
Erik Bacharach talks to Dan about the Titans and corona virus and contact tracing. Tom Curran tells Dan that the Malcolm Butler play at the end of the Super Bowl is the greatest play ever made in a Super Bowl.
